
To cleanly build the extension:
ant -Dextension.name=ezrecommendation clean-all build pack

To cleanly build the extension as trial edition:
ant -Dextension.name=ezrecommendation clean-all trial

To see all available options:
ant -Dextension.name=ezrecommendation -p


Results are in the build directory.

Dependencies:
ant, ant-contrib

